tory-installer/SKILL.md:101:| Atlassian API token (`https://id.atlassian.com/manage-profile/security/api-tokens`) | `JIRA_API_TOKEN` | non-empty |\\\\\\\\nskills/dark-factory-installer/SKILL.md:215:This is the only step that needs a one-time Chrome restart so we can attach to the user's logged-in Atlassian session.\\\\\\\\nskills/dark-factory-installer/SKILL.md:219:1. Tell the user clearly: *\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Quit Chrome completely (Cmd-Q). I'm going to relaunch it with remote debugging enabled so I can attach to your real Atlassian session. Your tabs and login will be preserved.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"* Wait for confirmation.\\\\\\\\nskills/dark-factory-installer/SKILL.md:220:2. Relaunch Chrome with the debug port pointing at the user's profile:\\\\\\\\nskills/dark-factory-installer/SKILL.md:227:4. **Drive Atlassian Automation via your browser MCP** (Cursor: `cursor-ide-browser`; Claude Code: `user-Playwright`). Navigate to:\\\\\\\\napp/settings.html:144:        <p class=\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"settings-status\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\">No shopping profile data yet.</p>\\\\\\\\nschemas/shopping-profile.schema.json:3:  \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"$id\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"https://shopping-assistent-factory.local/schemas/shopping-profile.schema.json\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\nschemas/shopping-profile.schema.json:19:      \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"Version of the shopping profile schema used by persisted profile data.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\nschemas/shopping-profile.schema.json:24:      \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 country code used for retailer availability, shipping, and sizing context.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\nschemas/shopping-profile.schema.json:29:      \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\": \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"ISO 4217 currency code used for all profile-level monetary values unless overridden.\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\\nschemas/shopping-profile.schema.json:83:      \\\\\\\\\\\\\\\"description\\\\\\\\\\\\\\\":